Chcete si ji koupit sama pro sebe?

480
00:48:06,116 --> 00:48:08,550
Ne, to je pro paní Han

481
00:48:08,752 --> 00:48:09,980
Pro paní Han?

482
00:48:10,454 --> 00:48:12,547
